{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she had a relationship with him that was humane.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was platonic, but it was very humane.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She saw him as a person, despite the fact that-- now what he told her was, and I don't know if this is true or not, but what he told her was that at the end, at the end, the SS had to, they were forced to enlist, that they did not do it.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know how the SS is hated because they did it on their own.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this is what he said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know if it was true or not, but my mother believed it, I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was your feelings of living so close to the SS men?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember other then, well, OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Other than remembering this about the children, other than identifying with my mother that this is a nice guy and you know he's to be talked with and he gives you things, I know that when we heard planes above, we'd always pray that they'd be Americans and not Germans.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, so we saw the Americans as liberators and the Germans as oppressors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But other than that, I don't think I had any, and I still don't have any, animosity toward individuals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I have tremendous feelings about what happened, but, but not individuals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I don't think I have any feelings that I recall anyway, except fear, fear of being discovered.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's nebulous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This unknown Nazi, or Hitler, oh, we hated Hitler-- OK, but anyway, speaking of having humane feelings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, this unknown Nazism was something to be terribly afraid of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the person right here who you know, I didn't have that feeling, other than those guys that were throwing the kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
